48:5Andnowthytwosons,EphraimandManasseh,whichwerebornunto
theeinthelandofEgyptbeforeIcameuntotheeintoEgypt,are
mine;asReubenandSimeon,theyshallbemine.
48:6Andthyissue,whichthoubegettestafterthem,shallbethine,
