isBethlehem.
48:8AndIsraelbeheldJoseph'ssons,andsaid,Whoarethese?48:9
AndJosephsaiduntohisfather,Theyaremysons,whomGodhathgiven
meinthisplace.Andhesaid,Bringthem,Ipraythee,untome,andI
willblessthem.
