15:12Andthewestborderwastothegreatsea,andthecoastthereof.
ThisisthecoastofthechildrenofJudahroundaboutaccordingto
theirfamilies.
15:13AnduntoCalebthesonofJephunnehhegaveapartamongthe
childrenofJudah,accordingtothecommandmentoftheLORDtoJoshua,
