himwillIgiveAchsahmydaughtertowife.
15:17AndOthnielthesonofKenaz,thebrotherofCaleb,tookit:and
hegavehimAchsahhisdaughtertowife.
15:18Anditcametopass,asshecameuntohim,thatshemovedhimto
askofherfatherafield:andshelightedoffherass;andCalebsaid
untoher,Whatwouldestthou?15:19Whoanswered,Givemeablessing;
forthouhastgivenmeasouthland;givemealsospringsofwater.
Andhegavehertheuppersprings,andthenethersprings.
15:20ThisistheinheritanceofthetribeofthechildrenofJudah
accordingtotheirfamilies.
