7:52ThechildrenofBesai,thechildrenofMeunim,thechildrenof
Nephishesim,7:53ThechildrenofBakbuk,thechildrenofHakupha,the
childrenofHarhur,7:54ThechildrenofBazlith,thechildrenof
Mehida,thechildrenofHarsha,7:55ThechildrenofBarkos,the
childrenofSisera,thechildrenofTamah,7:56Thechildrenof
Neziah,thechildrenofHatipha.
