yetthoudostdestroyme.
10:9Remember,Ibeseechthee,thatthouhastmademeastheclay;and
wiltthoubringmeintodustagain?10:10Hastthounotpouredmeout
asmilk,andcurdledmelikecheese?10:11Thouhastclothedmewith
skinandflesh,andhastfencedmewithbonesandsinews.
