takecomfortalittle,10:21BeforeIgowhenceIshallnotreturn,
eventothelandofdarknessandtheshadowofdeath;10:22Alandof
darkness,asdarknessitself;andoftheshadowofdeath,withoutany
order,andwherethelightisasdarkness.
