boweddownheavily,asonethatmournethforhismother.
35:15Butinmineadversitytheyrejoiced,andgatheredthemselves
together:yea,theabjectsgatheredthemselvestogetheragainstme,
andIknewitnot;theydidtearme,andceasednot:
35:16Withhypocriticalmockersinfeasts,theygnasheduponmewith
theirteeth.
