inherittheland:whenthewickedarecutoff,thoushaltseeit.
37:35Ihaveseenthewickedingreatpower,andspreadinghimself
likeagreenbaytree.
37:36Yethepassedaway,and,lo,hewasnot:yea,Isoughthim,but
hecouldnotbefound.
37:37Marktheperfectman,andbeholdtheupright:fortheendof
thatmanispeace.
37:38Butthetransgressorsshallbedestroyedtogether:theendof
thewickedshallbecutoff.
