time:OGod,inthemultitudeofthymercyhearme,inthetruthof
thysalvation.
69:14Delivermeoutofthemire,andletmenotsink:letmebe
deliveredfromthemthathateme,andoutofthedeepwaters.
69:15Letnotthewaterfloodoverflowme,neitherletthedeepswallow
meup,andletnotthepitshuthermouthuponme.
