mineenemies.
69:19Thouhastknownmyreproach,andmyshame,andmydishonour:
mineadversariesareallbeforethee.
69:20Reproachhathbrokenmyheart;andIamfullofheaviness:andI
lookedforsometotakepity,buttherewasnone;andforcomforters,
butIfoundnone.
69:21Theygavemealsogallformymeat;andinmythirsttheygave
mevinegartodrink.
