deliverhim,yetthoumustdoitagain.
19:20Hearcounsel,andreceiveinstruction,thatthoumayestbewise
inthylatterend.
19:21Therearemanydevicesinaman'sheart;neverthelessthe
counseloftheLORD,thatshallstand.
19:22Thedesireofamanishiskindness:andapoormanisbetter
thanaliar.
19:23ThefearoftheLORDtendethtolife:andhethathathitshall
abidesatisfied;heshallnotbevisitedwithevil.
