water:heturnethitwhithersoeverhewill.
21:2Everywayofamanisrightinhisowneyes:buttheLORD
pondereththehearts.
21:3TodojusticeandjudgmentismoreacceptabletotheLORDthan
sacrifice.
21:4Anhighlook,andaproudheart,andtheplowingofthewicked,
issin.
21:5Thethoughtsofthediligenttendonlytoplenteousness;butof
everyonethatishastyonlytowant.
