andfroofthemthatseekdeath.
21:7Therobberyofthewickedshalldestroythem;becausetheyrefuse
todojudgment.
21:8Thewayofmanisfrowardandstrange:butasforthepure,his
workisright.
21:9Itisbettertodwellinacornerofthehousetop,thanwitha
brawlingwomaninawidehouse.
21:10Thesoulofthewickeddesirethevil:hisneighbourfindethno
favourinhiseyes.
