3:11Woeuntothewicked!itshallbeillwithhim:fortherewardof
hishandsshallbegivenhim.
3:12Asformypeople,childrenaretheiroppressors,andwomenrule
overthem.Omypeople,theywhichleadtheecausetheetoerr,and
