Judahshallbecutoff:EphraimshallnotenvyJudah,andJudahshall
notvexEphraim.
11:14ButtheyshallflyupontheshouldersofthePhilistinestoward
thewest;theyshallspoilthemoftheeasttogether:theyshalllay
