18:4ForsotheLORDsaiduntome,Iwilltakemyrest,andIwill
considerinmydwellingplacelikeaclearheatuponherbs,andlikea
cloudofdewintheheatofharvest.
18:5Foraforetheharvest,whenthebudisperfect,andthesour
grapeisripeningintheflower,heshallbothcutoffthesprigswith
pruninghooks,andtakeawayandcutdownthebranches.
18:6Theyshallbelefttogetheruntothefowlsofthemountains,and
