ThereforeshallthestrengthofPharaohbeyourshame,andthetrust
intheshadowofEgyptyourconfusion.
30:4ForhisprinceswereatZoan,andhisambassadorscametoHanes.
30:5Theywereallashamedofapeoplethatcouldnotprofitthem,nor
beanhelpnorprofit,butashame,andalsoareproach.
