30:17Onethousandshallfleeattherebukeofone;attherebukeof
fiveshallyeflee:tillyebeleftasabeaconuponthetopofa
mountain,andasanensignonanhill.
30:18AndthereforewilltheLORDwait,thathemaybegraciousunto
you,andthereforewillhebeexalted,thathemayhavemercyupon
