thefruitfulvine.
32:13Uponthelandofmypeopleshallcomeupthornsandbriers;yea,
uponallthehousesofjoyinthejoyouscity:32:14Becausethe
palacesshallbeforsaken;themultitudeofthecityshallbeleft;
