Assyria.
37:11Behold,thouhastheardwhatthekingsofAssyriahavedoneto
alllandsbydestroyingthemutterly;andshaltthoubedelivered?
37:12Havethegodsofthenationsdeliveredthemwhichmyfathers
havedestroyed,asGozan,andHaran,andRezeph,andthechildrenof
