37:21ThenIsaiahthesonofAmozsentuntoHezekiah,saying,Thus
saiththeLORDGodofIsrael,Whereasthouhastprayedtomeagainst
SennacheribkingofAssyria:37:22ThisisthewordwhichtheLORD
