37:25Ihavedigged,anddrunkwater;andwiththesoleofmyfeet
haveIdriedupalltheriversofthebesiegedplaces.
37:26Hastthounotheardlongago,howIhavedoneit;andofancient
times,thatIhaveformedit?nowhaveIbroughtittopass,thatthou
shouldestbetolaywastedefencedcitiesintoruinousheaps.
