notcomeintothiscity,saiththeLORD.
37:35ForIwilldefendthiscitytosaveitformineownsake,and
formyservantDavid'ssake.
37:36ThentheangeloftheLORDwentforth,andsmoteinthecampof
theAssyriansahundredandfourscoreandfivethousand:andwhenthey
aroseearlyinthemorning,behold,theywerealldeadcorpses.
