lifeofmyspirit:sowiltthourecoverme,andmakemetolive.
38:17Behold,forpeaceIhadgreatbitterness:butthouhastinlove
tomysouldelivereditfromthepitofcorruption:forthouhastcast
allmysinsbehindthyback.
