executethmycounselfromafarcountry:yea,Ihavespokenit,Iwill
alsobringittopass;Ihavepurposedit,Iwillalsodoit.
46:12Hearkenuntome,yestouthearted,thatarefarfrom
righteousness:46:13Ibringnearmyrighteousness;itshallnotbe
faroff,andmysalvationshallnottarry:andIwillplacesalvation
