me?lo,theyallshallwaxoldasagarment;themothshalleatthem
up.
50:10WhoisamongyouthatfeareththeLORD,thatobeyeththevoice
ofhisservant,thatwalkethindarkness,andhathnolight?lethim
trustinthenameoftheLORD,andstayuponhisGod.
