everlastingkindnesswillIhavemercyonthee,saiththeLORDthy
Redeemer.
54:9ForthisisasthewatersofNoahuntome:forasIhavesworn
thatthewatersofNoahshouldnomoregoovertheearth;sohaveI
swornthatIwouldnotbewrothwiththee,norrebukethee.
54:10Forthemountainsshalldepart,andthehillsberemoved;butmy
kindnessshallnotdepartfromthee,neithershallthecovenantofmy
peaceberemoved,saiththeLORDthathathmercyonthee.
54:11Othouafflicted,tossedwithtempest,andnotcomforted,
behold,Iwilllaythystoneswithfaircolours,andlaythy
foundationswithsapphires.
