hislovingkindnesses.
63:8Forhesaid,Surelytheyaremypeople,childrenthatwillnot
lie:sohewastheirSaviour.
63:9Inalltheirafflictionhewasafflicted,andtheangelofhis
presencesavedthem:inhisloveandinhispityheredeemedthem;and
hebarethem,andcarriedthemallthedaysofold.
63:10Buttheyrebelled,andvexedhisholySpirit:thereforehewas
turnedtobetheirenemy,andhefoughtagainstthem.
63:11Thenherememberedthedaysofold,Moses,andhispeople,
saying,Whereishethatbroughtthemupoutoftheseawiththe
shepherdofhisflock?whereishethatputhisholySpiritwithin
