whichwalkethinawaythatwasnotgood,aftertheirownthoughts;
65:3Apeoplethatprovokethmetoangercontinuallytomyface;that
sacrificethingardens,andburnethincenseuponaltarsofbrick;65:4
Whichremainamongthegraves,andlodgeinthemonuments,whicheat
swine'sflesh,andbrothofabominablethingsisintheirvessels;
