childrenaregoneforthofme,andtheyarenot:thereisnoneto
stretchforthmytentanymore,andtosetupmycurtains.
10:21Forthepastorsarebecomebrutish,andhavenotsoughtthe
LORD:thereforetheyshallnotprosper,andalltheirflocksshallbe
