thingofnought,andthedeceitoftheirheart.
14:15ThereforethussaiththeLORDconcerningtheprophetsthat
prophesyinmyname,andIsentthemnot,yettheysay,Swordand
famineshallnotbeinthisland;Byswordandfamineshallthose
prophetsbeconsumed.
14:16Andthepeopletowhomtheyprophesyshallbecastoutinthe
streetsofJerusalembecauseofthefamineandthesword;andthey
shallhavenonetoburythem,them,theirwives,northeirsons,nor
theirdaughters:forIwillpourtheirwickednessuponthem.
