downwithtearsnightandday,andletthemnotcease:forthevirgin
daughterofmypeopleisbrokenwithagreatbreach,withavery
grievousblow.
14:18IfIgoforthintothefield,thenbeholdtheslainwiththe
sword!andifIenterintothecity,thenbeholdthemthataresick
