willnotshewyoufavour.
16:14Therefore,behold,thedayscome,saiththeLORD,thatitshall
nomorebesaid,TheLORDliveth,thatbroughtupthechildrenof
IsraeloutofthelandofEgypt;16:15But,TheLORDliveth,that
