17:4Andthou,eventhyself,shaltdiscontinuefromthineheritage
thatIgavethee;andIwillcausetheetoservethineenemiesinthe
landwhichthouknowestnot:foryehavekindledafireinmineanger,
whichshallburnforever.
17:5ThussaiththeLORD;Cursedbethemanthattrustethinman,and
makethfleshhisarm,andwhoseheartdepartethfromtheLORD.
