inthemidstofit,thathertimemaycome,andmakethidolsagainst
herselftodefileherself.
22:4Thouartbecomeguiltyinthybloodthatthouhastshed;andhast
defiledthyselfinthineidolswhichthouhastmade;andthouhast
causedthydaystodrawnear,andartcomeevenuntothyyears:
thereforehaveImadetheeareproachuntotheheathen,andamocking
toallcountries.
22:5Thosethatbenear,andthosethatbefarfromthee,shallmock
thee,whichartinfamousandmuchvexed.
