neitherknowethhim:butyeknowhim;forhedwellethwithyou,and
shallbeinyou.
14:18Iwillnotleaveyoucomfortless:Iwillcometoyou.
14:19Yetalittlewhile,andtheworldseethmenomore;butyesee
me:becauseIlive,yeshalllivealso.
14:20AtthatdayyeshallknowthatIaminmyFather,andyeinme,
andIinyou.
14:21Hethathathmycommandments,andkeepeththem,heitisthat
lovethme:andhethatlovethmeshallbelovedofmyFather,andI
